TextEng: Goodbye.
What will happen during this ritual?
I have questions about your fellows.
What gonna happen in spell?
Me gots questions about other peoples here.
Text: 여기 다른 사람들 얘기 물어볼 거 있어.

TextEng: I was happy to be part of the team.
Me glad to work with everyone.
How is Lord Nasher faring?
Lord Nasher okay? How he doing?
Why you kinda stop saying something? What you not say?
Text: 왜 말하다가 멈췄어? 뭐 안 말한 거 있어?

TextEng: Why did you hesitate to tell me something?
What form will the cure take?
What the cure gonna look like? Shiny?
Let's go back to my other questions.
We maybe go back to other questions?
Will your relationship with Aribeth improve now?
You maybe get along better with Aribeth now?
Desther will not create the cure alone. Others are involved.
Text: 데스터 혼자 치료약을 만드는 게 아냐. 다른 사람들도 연루되어 있어.

TextEng: Desther not make cure by himself. Others is helping.
Text: 데스터 혼자 치료제 못 만들어. 다른 사람들이 돕고 있어.

TextEng: I did the important part. Desther sat on his hands.
Text: 중요한 일은 내가 했습니다. 데스터는 손 놓고 있었죠.

TextEng: Me did important stuff. Desther just talk lots.
Text: 나 중요한 거 했어. 데스터는 말만 많았어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You can tell me. I've proven myself trustworthy.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 말해도 돼. 난 충분히 신뢰할 만하다는 걸 증명했잖아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> It okay to tell me. Ain't me proven good to trust?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 내게 말해도 돼. 나 믿을 만하단 거 증명했잖아, 안 그래?

TextEng: I am <race>, just as you are. I'll understand.
We both <race> kind. Me understand good.
Text: 우리 둘 다 <race>야. 나 잘 이해해.

TextEng: Tell me or I'll rip your head off!
You tells or me smash you flat!
Text: 말해, 아니면 널 납작하게 으깨버릴 거야!

TextEng: Have you done something to help him?
You done something to help him somehow?
Text: 그를 돕게 뭐 한 거 있어?

TextEng: Is there precedent for this? Will it work?
You understand it? It really work like that?
Doesn't that leave the castle unprotected?
Text: 그러면 성이 무방비 상태가 되는 거 아냐?

TextEng: That not make Castle Never weaker?
Text: 그럼 네버 성 더 약해지는 거 아냐?

TextEng: What would Aribeth think of this?
What Aribeth think of this, hmm? You not tell her?
Text: 아리베스 이거 뭐라 생각해, 흠? 그녀한테 말 안 했어?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Perhaps you see what you want to see.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 아무래도 당신은 보고 싶은 것만 보고있는 것 같군요.

TextEng: You keep secrets from her. That isn't a clue?
Text: 넌 그녀한테 비밀을 숨기고 있어. 그게 단서가 아니야?

TextEng: Yous keep secrets from her. You being dumb.
Text: 너 그녀한테 비밀 숨겨. 멍청한 거 아냐.
